BP: "Clique para Ativar/Desativar a exibição de caracteres ocidentais no jogo."
PL: "Kliknij, aby przełączyć na nieazjatyckie pogawędki etc."
END

GUI:AreYouSureDeleteAccount
US: "Are you sure you want to permanantly delete your account and all your saved statistics?"
