LAN:HostNotResponding
US: "Game exited; the host was not responding."
DE: "Spiel beendet. Der Host reagiert nicht."
FR: "Partie interrompue. Pas de réponse de l'hôte."
ES: "Saliendo del juego; el anfitrión no responde"
IT: "Uscita dalla partita, l'host non rispondeva"
KO: "게임을 취소합니다. 호스트가 응답하지 않습니다."
ZH: "離開遊戲，主機未有回應。"
BP: "Partida abandonada; o Host não estava respondendo"
PL: "Opuszczono sesję; gospodarz nie odpowiada"
END

LAN:PlayerDropped
US: "%ls dropped; player was not responding."
DE: "%ls ausgeschlossen; Spieler hat nicht reagiert"
