SCRIPT:CHI02AudioHolder20
US: "<AutoFerry Capt. speaking>\n'Finally, the military is here! Those Terrorists are ruining my business! If you put your forces aboard I'll take you out to the Convention Center. You can sneak in the backdoor and catch them by surprize. Jut hit the Transport button when you're ready.'"
DE: "<AutoFerry Capt. speaking>\n'Finally, the military is here! Those Terrorists are ruining my business! If you put your forces aboard I'll take you out to the Convention Center. You can sneak in the backdoor and catch them by surprize. Jut hit the Transport button when you're ready.'"
