BP: "Obrigado a todos os participantes do fantástico Teste Multijogador"
PL: "Wielkie podziękowania dla wszystkich uczestników testu gry wieloosobowej,"
END

CREDITS:MultiplayerTestParticipantThanxMessageLine2
US: "that helped us put the game through its paces. Your help has"
DE: "that helped us put the game through its paces. Your help has"
FR: "qui nous ont permis de mettre le jeu au point. Votre aide a"
ES: "que nos ayudaron a poner en marcha el juego. Vuestra ayuda"
IT: "che ci hanno aiutato ad apportare le ultime rifiniture al gioco. Il vostro aiuto è"
KO: "that helped us put the game through its paces. Your help has"
ZH: "that helped us put the game through its paces. Your help has"
BP: "que nos ajudaram a colocar este jogo nos trilhos. Sua ajuda foi"
PL: "którzy pomogli nam w sprawdzaniu gry. Wasza pomoc"
END

CREDITS:MultiplayerTestParticipantThanxMessageLine3
US: "been invaluable and we hope you enjoyed the experience."
DE: "been invaluable and we hope you enjoyed the experience."
FR: "été précieuse et nous espérons que vous avez apprécié l'expérience."
ES: "ha sido incalculable y esperamos que hayáis disfrutado con la experiencia."
IT: "stato molto prezioso e speriamo che vi siate anche divertiti."
KO: "been invaluable and we hope you enjoyed the experience."
ZH: "been invaluable and we hope you enjoyed the experience."
BP: "muito importante, e esperamos que tenham curtido a experiência."
PL: "była nieoceniona i mamy nadzieję, że dla Was było to ciekawe doświadczenie."
END

CREDITS:SpecialThanxKeyMessage1
US: "A very special thanks to all of our families for allowing us to do what"
DE: "A very special thanks to all of our families for allowing us to do what"
FR: "Un remerciement très spécial à toutes nos familles pour nous\navoir laissé faire ce que nous aimons : créer des jeux."
ES: "Gracias especialmente a nuestras familias por dejarnos hacer"
IT: "Un ringraziamento speciale alle nostre famiglie, che ci hanno permesso di fare ciò"
KO: "A very special thanks to all of our families for allowing us to do what"
ZH: "A very special thanks to all of our families for allowing us to do what"
BP: "Um obrigado muito especial para nossas famílias, por permitirem que façamos"
PL: "Bardzo specjalne podziękowania dla naszych rodzin, za to,"
END

CREDITS:SpecialThanxKeyMessage2
US: "we love: making games. We can't thank you enough for your support."
DE: "we love: making games. We can't thank you enough for your support."
FR: "Nous ne pourrons jamais vous remercier assez pour votre soutien."
ES: "lo que nos apasiona: crear juegos. No nos cansamos de agradeceros vuestro apoyo."
IT: "che ci piace: creare giochi. Non vi ringrazieremo mai abbastanza."
KO: "we love: making games. We can't thank you enough for your support."
ZH: "we love: making games. We can't thank you enough for your support."
BP: "o que amamos: criar jogos. Não há como agradecer o suficiente seu apoio."
PL: "że pozwalały nam pracować nad grą. Żadne słowa nie wyrażą naszej wdzięczności."
END

CREDITS:SpecialThanxKeyMessage3
US: "But we'll try..."
DE: "But we'll try..."
FR: "Mais nous essayerons…"
ES: "Así que ahí va..."
IT: "Ma ci proveremo…"
KO: "But we'll try..."
ZH: "But we'll try..."
BP: "Mas tentaremos...."
PL: "Ale spróbujemy…"
END

CREDITS:SpecialThanx6Line1
US: "Thanks to my better half, Tawny Pham. Your patience"
DE: "Thanks to my better half, Tawny Pham. Your patience"
FR: "Merci à ma moitié, Tawny Pham. Ta patience"
ES: "Gracias a mi media naranja, Tawny Pham. Sin tu paciencia"
IT: "Grazie alla mia dolce metà, Tawny Pham. La tua pazienza"
KO: "Thanks to my better half, Tawny Pham. Your patience"
ZH: "Thanks to my better half, Tawny Pham. Your patience"
BP: "Obrigado a minha cara metade, Tawny Pham. Sua paciência"
PL: "Dziękuję mojej lepszej połowie, Tawny Pham. Twoja cierpliwość"
END

CREDITS:SpecialThanx6Line2
US: "& support have been invaluable. I love you dearly."
DE: "& support have been invaluable. I love you dearly."
FR: "et ton soutien ont été inestimables. Je t'aime tendrement."
ES: "y apoyo habría sido imposible. Te quiero muchísimo."
IT: "e il tuo sostegno mi sono stati molto preziosi. Ti amo."
KO: "& support have been invaluable. I love you dearly."
ZH: "& support have been invaluable. I love you dearly."
BP: "& apoio foram fundamentais. Te amo muito."
PL: "i wsparcie były nieocenione. Bardzo Cię kocham."
END

